The '''Oil Refinery''' converts raw [[Main/en/Oil]] into [[Main/en/Goods]].

It can only be positioned near the edges of a map, even when using [[Main/en/Industries|Fund New Industry]]. This is due to a [[Main/en/Oil refinery limit|setting in openttd.cfg]].

Oil Refineries can be destroyed by the [[Main/en/Disaster#Oil refinery explosion|military jet disaster]], but will rebuild itself soon.

